      "writtenOn": "2020-08-05T22:34:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Did you notice on that 1-space CL that the tool totally misunderstood a few files and reformatted them very weirdly?  Any idea what\u0027s up with that?  Is that specific to 1-space, or did you fix up its bad output for the 2-space CL?",
      "parentUuid": "c460cf9e_5adef1de",
      "revId": "dde007319df1ede7737cacf1ceb3f0c9444db942",
